      "writtenOn": "2019-08-19T18:05:40Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Writing to GCS takes a long time.  The idea is for UpdateCallback to asynchronously request a write and return immediately. If we held the mutex while we called write, then any calls to UpdateCallback would block until we were done.",
